name: Air Canada Boeing 777-200LR Landing and Takeoff at Calgary Airport
description:
The holiday heavies continue! We get Air Canada's Boeing 777-200LR most summers on our Calgary to Frankfurt route thanks to its cargo capabilities, but it's always a pleasure to see it out of season. Here we have C-FNND arriving from Toronto as "Air Canada 139 heavy" on runway 17L, and departing a few hours later back to YYZ as "Air Canada 146 heavy" off of 17R, with YouTuber tprfilms on board. ATC is included!

Thanks for watching!
